<div class="lesson">
  <h2 id="unit-1-4">Lesson 4: Making Links - HTML Attributes:</h2>
  <p class="content">
    Make links in html using the Anchor tag
  </p>
  <div class="example">
    <h3>Example:</h3>
    Anchor tag - <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> = <code>&lt;a href="value"&gt;contents&lt;/a&gt;</code>
    <p>1) I am going to learn to love <a href="www.w3c.org/html">HTML</a><br>
      2) This website is <a href="https://www.udacity.com">my favorite</a></p>
